-         * CAPABILITY_SLICES_PER_FRAME(2) ÔÇô hint the host encoder to split each frame into
-         *   2 slices so the A9 Gen4 HW decoder can start decoding the first slice while
-         *   the second is still arriving over the network (pipeline parallelism).
+         *   causes latency spikes at high bitrates.  Without _AV1, Sunshine sets
